<para style="p">

  <verse number="1" style="v" />Therefore, when we could no longer bear it, we thought it was good to be left behind at Athens alone.

  <verse number="2" style="v" />We sent Timothy, our brother and fellow worker for God in the gospel of Christ, to strengthen and comfort you regarding your faith.

<note caller="+" style="f">

  <char style="ft">Some other versions read, </char>

  <char style="fqa">We sent Timothy, our brother and God's servant in the gospel of Christ. </char>

</note>

  <verse number="3" style="v" />We did this so that no one would be shaken by these sufferings. For yourselves know that for this we have been appointed.
